!!!5
html
  head
    title Absorption - A game made for Ludum Dare #24
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="stylesheets/application.css")
    link(href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Enriqueta:400,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')

    script(src="javascripts/lib/jquery.js")
    script(src="javascripts/lib/jquery.cookie.js")
    script(src="javascripts/lib/underscore.js")
    script(src="javascripts/lib/jwerty.js")
    script(src="javascripts/lib/eventemitter.js")
    script(src="javascripts/lib/soundmanager2-jsmin.js")

    script(src="javascripts/ld24/screen.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/game.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/sounds.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/scenes/splashscene.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/scenes/introscene.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/scenes/gamescene.js")

    script(src="javascripts/ld24/mob.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/mobs/player.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/mobs/mote.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/mobs/powerup.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/mobs/powerup_speed.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/mobs/powerup_attraction.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/mobs/bad.js")

    script(src="javascripts/ld24/particle.js")

    script(src="javascripts/ld24/level.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/levels/1.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/levels/2.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/levels/3.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/levels/4.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/levels/5.js")
    script(src="javascripts/ld24/levels/endless.js")

    script(src="javascripts/application.js")
  body
    .canvas-wrapper
      canvas
      .debug Debug
      .version

      .level-progress
        .level Level 1
        .progress
          .done

      .level-complete
      .level-complete-detail

      .continue Press [ENTER] to try again.

      .info-box
        .icon !
        .text

        .close

      .ingame-menu
        .paused Game paused.
        ul.menu
          li.continue.active Continue
          li.retry Retry
          li.quit Quit

      .splash
        a(href="https://github.com/saschagehlich/ld24", target="_blank")
          img(style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; border: 0;", src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/github/ribbons/forkme_right_white_ffffff.png", alt="Fork me on GitHub")

        .logo Absorption

        ul.menu
          li.campaign.active Tutorial
          li.endless Endless Game
          li.about About

        .copyright 
          |Crafted with love and caffeine by Sascha Gehlich (
          a(href="http://twitter.com/rattazong", target="_blank") @rattazong
          |) for Ludum Dare #24 (in <48 hours)

      .intro
        .filsh-media
          img.logo(src="assets/images/fm-logo.png")
          .text
            img(src="assets/images/fm-logotext.png")

          img.mob(src="assets/images/mob-rendered.png")

        img.ld(src="assets/images/ld-logo.png")

      .about
        h3 About "Absorption"

        p 
          | Absorption is a game created for the 24th 
          a(href="http://ludumdare.com", target="_blank") Ludum Dare
          |  game competition within less than 48 hours.

        p 
          strong Nerd facts:

        ul.nerd-facts
          li 
            | - Written in 
            a(href="http://coffeescript.org", target="_blank") CoffeeScript
            | , a language that compiles to JavaScript
          li - Does not use any graphics libraries, everything written from scratch
          li 
            | - Uses the following libraries: 
            a(href="http://jquery.com", target="_blank") jQuery
            | , 
            a(href="http://keithcirkel.co.uk/jwerty/", target="_blank") jwerty
            | , 
            a(href="http://underscorejs.org", target="_blank") underscore.js
            | , 
            a(href="http://www.schillmania.com/projects/soundmanager2/", target="_blank") SoundManager 2

          li 
            | - It is open source and available on 
            a(href="http://github.com/saschagehlich/ld24", target="_blank") github.com
            |.

        p All graphics content has been created using Photoshop CS5.
        p All audio content has been created using Audacity and Ableton Live.

        .back Back to menu